snippet.title: Detective Pikachu Returns - Nintendo Direct 6.21.2023
snippet.description:
Solve mysteries with the personality-packed Detective Pikachu in Detective Pikachu Returns, coming to Nintendo Switch on October 6! Pre-order today: https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/detective-pikachu-returns-switch/
